## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Build process: Run `npm run build` locally in the `web` folder to ensure no type/syntax errors block the deployment.

### Manual Verification
- Visual consistency check: Ensure all pages employ the shared standard `hc-` tokens, specifically avoiding arbitrary padding, margins, or color hex values not part of the design system.
- Regression check: Validate that mock data connections, states, and functionality (hooks, inputs) still work identically.
